name: PilA
title: type IV Pilus major pilin PilA

name: PilB
title: type IV Pilus minor pilin PilAB

name: XcpQ
title: T2SS general secretion pathway secretin XcpQ

name: OprM
title: MDR efflux porin OprM
description: MexAB-OprM is constitutively expressed under lab growth conditions [@Adewoye:2002jm]

name: OprJ
title: MDR efflux porin OprJ
description: MexCD-OprJ is not expressed in WT cells [@Li:2015fx]

name: OprN
title: MDR efflux porin OprN
description: MexEF-OprN is not expressed in WT cells [@Li:2015fx]

name: OprOP
title: phosphate uptake porins OprO and OprP
description: induced in phosphate limitation [@Hancock:1982if]. The two porins are structurally similar and have immunologic cross-reactivity. [@Chevalier:2017ck]

name: OpdH
title: cis-aconitate uptake porin OpdH
description: upregulated only in presence of substrates (e.g. cis-aconitate and vanillate) [@Taylor:2019cn]; [@Tamber:2007gh]

name: OprD
title: amino acid transporter porin OprD
description: major porin. frequently lost in infection isolates; loss confers carbapenem (esp. imipenem) resistance, fitness advantage [@Skurnik:2013ja].

name: OprB
title: glucose uptake porin OprB
description: 50x downregulated in biofilms vs. planktonic cells [@Chevalier:2017cka]

name: MexAB
title: RND-type multidrug efflux pump MexAB
description: MexAB-OprM is constitutively expressed under lab growth conditions [@Adewoye:2002jm]

name: MexCD
title: RND-type multidrug efflux pump MexCD
description: MexCD-OprJ is not expressed in WT cells [@Li:2015fx]

name: MexEF
title: RND-type multidrug efflux pump MexEF
description: MexEF-OprN is not expressed in WT cells [@Li:2015fx]

name: LPS-galU
title: truncated outer core oligosaccharide, uncapped LPS
